SELECT
  id,
  SUM((r = 0) * c) AS p0,
  SUM((r = 1) * c) AS p1,
  SUM((r = 2) * c) AS p2
FROM (
  SELECT
    id, r,
    COUNT(*) AS c
  FROM (
    SELECT
      discussion_id AS id,
      react as r
    FROM discussion_reacts
  )
  GROUP BY id, r
)
GROUP BY id

SELECT who.id, which, who FROM (
  SELECT '000000000000000' as id, name as which FROM which
  ORDER BY RANDOM()
  LIMIT 1) as which
JOIN (
  SELECT '000000000000000' as id, name as who FROM who
  ORDER BY RANDOM()
  LIMIT 1) as who
ON which.id = who.id
